OL,3,CDownload Festival organisers announce
OL,4,Cnew measures after 2023 traffic chaos
OL,6,FOrganisers of 2024 have announced new
OL,7,Fmeasures to help reduce traffic delays.
OL,9,FIt comes after last year's event, held
OL,10,Fat Donington Park in and attended by
OL,11,F100,000 people, caused chaos on the
OL,12,Fsurrounding roads and motorways,
OL,14,FFestival organisers have told ITV News
OL,15,FCentral that this year they will be
OL,16,Fintroducing new measures - including
OL,17,Fhaving two arrival days and a new team
OL,18,Fof traffic coordinators.
