OL,3,CDownload Festival organisers announce
OL,4,Cnew measures after 2023 traffic chaos
OL,6,F100,000 rock fans made their way to
OL,7,Fthe site for the festival's 20th
OL,8,Fanniversary last year - many driving
OL,9,Fon the M1, A50, A42, A38 and A453.
OL,11,FDrivers were warned of "severe
OL,12,Fcongestion" by National Highways with
OL,13,Fa minimum of two hour delays - many
OL,14,Fdrivers reported they're were stuck
OL,15,Ffor up to five hours.
OL,17,F2024 festival organiser, Jess Shields,
OL,18,Fsaid this year there will be two
OL,19,Farrival days so traffic will be spread
OL,20,Fout, as well as less than 100,000
OL,21,Fattendees.
